44; Trenberth, K.E., Dai, A., Rasmussen, R.M., Parsons, D.B., The changing character of precipitation (2003) Bull. Amer. Meteor. Soc., 84, pp. 1205-1217; Trenberth, K.E., (2007) Observations Surface and atmospheric climate change. Climate Change 2007 The Physical Science Basis, pp. 235-336. , S. Solomon et al., Eds., Cambridge University Press; Vecchi, G.A., Soden, B.J., Global warming and the weakening of the tropical circulation (2007) J. Climate, 20, pp. 4316-4340; Vecchi, G.A., Soden, B.J., Wittenberg, A.T., Held, I.M., Leetmaa, A., Harrison, M.J., Weakening of tropical Pacific atmospheric circulation due to anthropogenic forcing (2006) Nature, 441, pp. 73-76; Wentz, F.J., Ricciardulli, L., Hilburn, K., Mears, C., How much more rain will global warming bring? (2007) Science, 317, pp. 233-235; Yu, J.-Y., Neelin, J.D., Modes of tropical variability under convective adjustment and the Madden-Julian oscillation Part II Numerical results (1994) J. Atmos. Sci., 51, pp. 1895-1914; Yu, J.-Y., Chou, C., Neelin, J.D., Estimating the gross moist stability of the tropical atmosphere (1998) J. Atmos. Sci., 55, pp. 1354-1372; Zeng, N., Neelin, J.D., Chou, C., A quasi-equilibrium tropical circulation model-Implementation and simulation (2000) J. Atmos. Sci., 57, pp. 1767-1796","Chou, C.; Research Center for Environmental Changes, Academia Sinica, P.O. Box 1-48, Taipei 11529, Taiwan; email: chiachou@rcec.sinica.edu.tw",,,,,,,,08948755,,,,"English","J. Clim.",Article,Scopus,2-s2.0-77954358191
